    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients undergoing a tonsillectomy

          -  Patients undergoing an adenotonsillectomy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  All patients with a known history of bleeding or clotting disorders, as well as those
             patients who had presented to Nationwide Children's Hospital main operating room for
